tbtcToBtc(address,bytes8,bytes20,address.details: Vending Machine transfers TBTC allowance to Deposit.

params._depositAddress: The address of the Deposit to redeem.
params._finalRecipient: The deposit redeemer. This address will receive the TDT.
params._outputValueBytes: The 8-byte Bitcoin transaction output size in Little Endian.
params._requesterPKH: The 20-byte Bitcoin pubkeyhash to which to send funds.

params._tdtId: ID of tBTC Deposit Token to buy

params._tdtId: ID of tBTC Deposit Token to sell
